==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: Thirty years on the east side of the river, thirty years on the west side of the river.

===Pronunciation===
*[[Pinyin]]: sān shí nián hé dōng, sān shí nián hé xī

===Proverb===
'''[[三]][[十]][[年]][[河]][[東]]，[[三]][[十]][[年]][[河]][[西]]'''

# Prosperity and decline never last.
# Life has its ups and downs.
# Everything in life is cyclical.
# Easy come, easy go.

===Alternate forms===
[[三]][[十]][[年]][[河]][[东]]，[[三]][[十]][[年]][[河]][[西]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])

